== Micro Bar Chart as a status component ==

{{Template:fluidops:StatusPercentMicroBarchart | percent = 77}}
{{Template:fluidops:StatusPercentMicroBarchart | percent = 8}}
{{Template:fluidops:StatusPercentMicroBarchart | percent = 30}}

==== Code ====
<div style="width:40%;">
<source>{{Template:StatusPercentMicroBarchart | percent = 77}}</source>
</div>
