</div>

=== Using dynamic evaluation ===

Often the actual arguments for the charts have to be computed. This can be achieved using the [[Help:QueryResult]].

{{#widget: QueryResult | 
 template = 'Template:fluidops:StatusPercentMicroBarchart'
 | query = 'SELECT * WHERE { BIND("42" AS ?percent) }'
 | format = 'TEMPLATE_PAGE'
}}

<source>
{{#widget: QueryResult | 
 template = 'Template:fluidops:StatusPercentMicroBarchart'
 | query = 'SELECT * WHERE { BIND("42" AS ?percent) }'
 | format = 'TEMPLATE_PAGE'
}}
</source>
